homestead-app/
│
├── index.html              → Dashboard overview
├── garden.html             → Gardening, planting zones, seed data
├── pantry.html             → Recipes, food storage, preservation logs
├── survival.html           → Tools, bug-out gear, emergency kits
├── weather.html            → Weather, moon phase, forecasts
│
├── assets/
│   ├── images/
│   ├── icons/
│   └── videos/
│
├── css/
│   └── style.css
│
├── js/
│   ├── main.js             → Shared scripts (nav, theming, etc.)
│   ├── garden.js           → Zone calculator, seed planner
│   ├── pantry.js           → Recipe gallery, timers, etc.
│   └── survival.js         → Tool list, embedded video links
│
└── data/
    ├── seeds.json          → USDA zone recommendations
    ├── recipes.json        → Recipe data
    ├── tools.json          → Survival gear links & info
    └── contacts.json       → Emergency contact data

README.md                   → Project overview and instructions